              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "۳۹۱. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): ازْهَدْ فِي"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:450:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/391/489",
        "text": [
          " الدُّنْيَا يُبَصّرْكَ اللهُ عَوْرَاتِهَا، وَلَا تَغْفُلْ فَلَسْتَ بِمَغْفُولٍ عَنْكَ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "391. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Abstain from the world so that Allāh may show you its real evils and do not be neglectful because (in any case) you will not be neglected."
          ]
        }
      }
